# .dockerignore — keep build context minimal.
#
# The Dockerfile currently does not COPY anything from the build
# context (the project is bind-mounted at runtime), so this list is
# defensive: if a future revision starts COPYing source in, none of
# these should ride along.

**/node_modules
**/.venv
**/dist
**/.astro
**/.smoke
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
.git
.github
.vscode
*.log

# never bake secrets into an image
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
